# ENTITY::IS_ENTITY_ATTACHED

## Summary
Returns true if the entity is attached to anything (another entity or the world)

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Whether the entity is attached to any other entity.
